subSubSection.paragraph:
Abdomen (
Fig. 76c
): Tergites with posterior area brown with scattered irregular pale marks, but anterior area mostly pale with few dark brown marks. Sternites in general entirely pale, but some specimens with few dark brown marks in some sternites. Tergites and distal sternites set with short black setae, remaining sternites covered with short white setae.
